1. 问题: 对比各公司在2021年新增与2021年更新的服务区数量：输出公司名称、2021年新建数、2021年更新数、差值（新建减更新）
   原始错误: trailing junk after numeric literal 在 "2021年新建数" 或附近的
LINE 1: ...pany_name AS 公司名称, COALESCE(t1.cnt_new, 0) AS 2021年新建...
                                                             ^
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT c.company_name AS "公司名称", COALESCE(t1.cnt_new, 0) AS "2021年新建数", COALESCE(t2.cnt_upd, 0) AS "2021年更新数", COALESCE(t1.cnt_new, 0) - COALESCE(t2.cnt_upd, 0) AS "新建减更新差值" FROM public.bss_company c LEFT JOIN (SELECT sa.company_id, COUNT(*) AS cnt_new FROM public.bss_service_area sa WHERE sa.delete_ts IS NULL AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM sa.create_ts) = 2021 GROUP BY sa.company_id) t1 ON c.id = t1.company_id LEFT JOIN (SELECT sa.company_id, COUNT(*) AS cnt_upd FROM public.bss_service_area sa WHERE sa.delete_ts IS NULL AND EXTRACT(YEAR FROM sa.update_ts) = 2021 GROUP BY sa.company_id) t2 ON c.id = t2.company_id WHERE c.delete_ts IS NULL ORDER BY "新建减更新差值" DESC;
