8. 问题: 近15天内，订单量环比下降最明显的前3个餐饮档口及其下降幅度
   原始错误: 字段 "branch_id" 不存在
LINE 1: EXPLAIN WITH recent AS (SELECT branch_id, SUM(order_sum) AS ...
                                       ^
HINT:  也许您想要引用列"bss_business_day_data.branch_no"。
   修复后SQL:
   WITH recent AS (SELECT branch_no, SUM(order_sum) AS total_orders FROM bss_business_day_data WHERE oper_date >= CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '15 day' GROUP BY branch_no), last_week AS (SELECT branch_no, SUM(order_sum) AS orders_lw FROM bss_business_day_data WHERE oper_date BETWEEN CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '15 day' AND CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '8 day' GROUP BY branch_no), this_week AS (SELECT branch_no, SUM(order_sum) AS orders_tw FROM bss_business_day_data WHERE oper_date > CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '8 day' GROUP BY branch_no) SELECT br.branch_name AS 档口名称, ROUND(100.0 * (COALESCE(t.orders_tw, 0) - COALESCE(l.orders_lw, 0)) / NULLIF(l.orders_lw, 0), 2) AS 下降幅度 FROM recent r JOIN bss_branch br ON r.branch_no = br.branch_no LEFT JOIN last_week l ON r.branch_no = l.branch_no LEFT JOIN this_week t ON r.branch_no = t.branch_no WHERE br.classify = '餐饮' AND l.orders_lw > 0 ORDER BY 下降幅度 ASC LIMIT 3;
----------------------------------------
